The paper deals with optimization of power allocation and precoding for multi-cell processing with limited cooperation, which is a topic that falls under the field of information theory (cs.IT). The paper also discusses channel state information (CSI) and proposes a two-way channel estimation process, which is relevant to the field of networked systems (cs.NI) and control systems (cs.SY). The paper also mentions multiple input multiple output (MIMO) channels, which is a topic in multimedia (cs.MM). Finally, the paper discusses optimal designs and mutual information, which are topics in machine learning (cs.LG).
